# The growing sample archive lives in Git LFS so the repo (and the submodule
# consumers) stay lean. The curated corpus/ pcaps are PLAIN git on purpose —
# they are small (minimized to the Initials) and must always be present for the
# self-test. Only samples/ pcaps are LFS-backed.
samples/**/*.pcap   filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
samples/**/*.pcapng filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
